items.name: Meet the Birds
items.text: New York certainly has plenty of whacky birds, just go find your rent controlled neighbor or favorite hobo to see what we're talking about. To meet some truly exotic and actual birds however, we recommend heading to Bryant Park for an up-and-close visit with some of NY's most beautiful creatures of the sky.
